title: DDFP 460:  Terrell Owens Hall of Fame Debate & QB Controversies
itunes:title: DDFP 460:  Terrell Owens Hall of Fame Debate & QB Controversies
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank & Patrick Claybon to discuss whether Terrell Owens should be in the hall of fame and who they feel is the 2nd best WR of all-time.  The guys also tackle LeBron’s legacy & predict who will win the NBA Finals.  Plus, Hank and Shek compete in another surprise game show, Kyle Long is back for the latest edition of Killin’ Time and the guys wrap with a chat about the past episode of “Game of Thrones.”
